The paper is focused on face recognition and generation, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also involves database retrieval and assembly of components, which could be categorized under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses the importance of considering human perception and description, which could be relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
